      "message": "The names of these properties are not clear to me.\nthe file is sdc.properties and the config item says server port.  to me that says that some sdc server is listening on 9530 which isn't true. There are many charts that listen on port 9530.  it might be a little clearer if you use the value key for the sdc context builder chart like you do above.  Why not use .Values.config.sdcCtxBuilderExternalPort or something to that effect.",
